text:
All Plant to be provided shall be manufactured and all work to be done under the Contract shall be carried out
(a) in the manner set out in the Contract;
(b) in a proper, workmanlike and careful manner in accordance with recognised good practices;
(c) with properly equipped facilities and (unless otherwise specified in the Contract) without using hazardous materials; and
(d) to the satisfaction of the Supervision Consultant and the Project Manager.
Inspection and Testing

